Arrietty...

533
01:30:08,793 --> 01:30:11,751
You take care of yourself.

534
01:30:14,293 --> 01:30:15,584
Goodbye.

535
01:30:19,501 --> 01:30:24,584
Arrietty, you're in my heart now and for always.

536
01:30:24,709 --> 01:30:27,918
I'll never forget you, ever.

537
